VISTA.TEXT: SELECT p.c_pjurrea_id, p.a_campo, DECODE (g.C_PJURREA_ID, NULL, 'S', 'N') b_cargable FROM (SELECT c_PJURREA_ID, a_campo FROM p_juridicas_rea, campo_rea) p, (SELECT c_PJURREA_ID, a_campo FROM pjur#campo#error pjce, error_rea e WHERE pjce.c_error = e.c_error AND c_caracter = 'G') g WHERE p.c_PJURREA_id = g.c_PJURREA_id(+) AND p.a_campo = g.a_campo(+)

SELECT FR.C_FICHREA_ID, DECODE(G.C_FICHREA_ID, NULL, 'S', 'N') B_CARGABLE FROM FICHERO_REA FR, (SELECT distinct C_FICHREA_ID FROM FICHERO#ERROR FE, ERROR_REA E WHERE FE.C_ERROR = E.C_ERROR AND E.C_CARACTER = 'G') G WHERE FR.C_FICHREA_ID = G.C_FICHREA_ID (+)

SELECT pj.c_pjurrea_id, DECODE (campo.C_PJURREA_ID, NULL, 'S', 'N') b_cargable FROM p_juridicas_rea pj, (SELECT C_PJURREA_ID FROM error_rea e, pjur#error pje WHERE pje.c_error = e.c_error AND c_caracter = 'G' union SELECT c_PJURREA_ID FROM pjur#campo#error WHERE c_error IN ('09', '10')) campo WHERE pj.c_PJURrea_id = campo.c_PJURrea_id(+)
